.TH man 1 "2022-10-12" "0.13.0" "Profanity XMPP client"

.SH NAME
/alias

.SH DESCRIPTION
Add, remove or list command aliases.

.SH SYNOPSIS
/alias list

.LP
/alias add <name> <value>

.LP
/alias remove <name>

.LP

.SH ARGUMENTS
.PP
\fBlist\fR
.RS 4
List all aliases.
.RE
.PP
\fBadd <name> <value>\fR
.RS 4
Add a new command alias.
.RE
.PP
\fBremove <name>\fR
.RS 4
Remove a command alias.
.RE

.SH EXAMPLES
/alias add friends /who online friends

.LP
/alias add /q /quit

.LP
/alias add a /away "I'm in a meeting."

.LP
/alias remove q

.LP
/alias list

.LP
